{"tid":1613380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧小平：殺200人保20年穩定","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T18:25:21.000Z","uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd388fec1710d7300dc5f575557ead7cf38d9059","tid":1613380,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"鄧小平：殺200人保20年穩定<br />\n2016-12-31<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】坊間盛傳鄧小平在六四事件中說過「殺20萬人，保20年穩定」。英國解密檔案揭露，八九民運期間中共早於5月已準備血腥鎮壓學生。當時英國駐華大使唐納德得悉鄧小平5月曾說「殺200人，保中國20年穩定」。他又引述美國國防部門稱，中國政府認為這場運動將流血收場。<br />\n1989年5月20日，即中國宣佈戒嚴當天，唐納德向英發出密電匯報當地情況。當天唐與著名漢學家施拉姆（Stuart Schram）共晉午餐，施表示有中方人士向他透露，近日鄧小平說過殺200人可保20年穩定，反映中共不惜犧牲部份示威者性命以穩定局勢，並換取時間達致中國改革開放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1989年5月，漢學家施拉姆向英駐華大使引述中方消息，稱鄧小平曾指「殺200人，保中國20年穩定」（紅框示）。英國檔案處文件<br />\n<br />\n美情報證京早準備鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n唐納德在密電續稱，本來對施拉姆消息有保留，但當晚美國國防部門也傳來情報，指中國政府認為沒任何方法避免死傷（no way to avoid blooodshed）；中國政府已下令政府醫院員工上班；軍方亦接獲指示，須採取必要手段平定局勢。唐再向美空軍查核真偽，確認消息來源非常可信。<br />\n六四期間任《文匯報》駐京辦主任的劉銳紹指密電沒指明鄧的說話來自哪位中方人士，難以評真偽。他形容1989年5月起北京謠言滿天飛，如「成日有人話坦克會開落廣場，結果狼來了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161231/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161231%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=1d802d51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afbd18722778b5fb22767fc5aac75946b2e87202","tid":1613380,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f